- Use TEXT to assist: Grammar, Vocabulary analysis
- If audio differs from text, trust the AUDIO.
"""
    else:
        input_section = """## Input
[Listen to the attached audio and transcribe it first]
"""

    return f"""{history_section}{profile_section}{input_section}
Execute "Linguistic Audit" per System instructions. Return JSON immediately.
"""


